Prefers forests of the Colchic (= Colchian) type admixed with beech, chestnut, and rhododendron (
Rhododendron ponticum
). Activity of imago proceeds from April until July. Carabus (Archiplectes) koltzei koltzei Rost, 1889, Carabus (Megodontus) septemcarinatus Motschulsky, 1840, and Carabus (Sphodristocarabus) armeniacus laevilineatus Ganglbauer, 1887, also occur together with this species (being much more abundant).
